and doesn't understand the world.

173
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:44,159
As her elder brother,

174
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,600
I can't allow her to commit

175
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:49,559
such a rebellious act as elopement.

176
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:51,759
Shen Qingtang,

177
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:54,240
come here now.

178
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,120
It was my idea.

179
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:57,660
It has nothing to do with Qingtang.

180
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:03,320
Such deep affection
from you is touching.

181
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:05,360
Qingtang,

182
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,559
why not take this chance

183
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,559
to speak your true thoughts

184
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,840
from this past while?

185
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,480
Think carefully.

186
00:09:23,759 --> 00:09:24,759
If you really leave,

187
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,480
there are some people

188
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,320
you'll never be able
to see again in this lifetime.

189
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:48,460
Thank you for your love, Your Highness.

190
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:50,480
But unfortunately,

191
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,000
