197
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,159
Come with me.

198
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:13,840
Your Highness,

199
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:16,759
I never

200
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,559
had true feelings for you.

201
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:25,480
She merely coveted the power
of Lord Pingnan Manor

202
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,240
and desired wealth and status.

203
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,159
Qingtang.

204
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,759
I don't believe it.

205
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,840
Why would you suddenly say such things?

206
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:40,799
Then what about all

207
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,000
