208
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:49,240
I grew tired of being an adopted girl.

209
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:52,480
I just want to be a noble lady.

210
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:54,919
Marrying you

211
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,970
or marrying someone else

212
00:10:59,399 --> 00:11:00,240
is all the same.

